OL,3,CAuthorities repeatedly warned about
OL,4,Cterrorist's mental health, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FAn inquest into the deaths of three
OL,8,Fmen stabbed to death in Reading has
OL,9,Fheard authorities were repeatedly
OL,10,Fwarned about the terrorist's mental
OL,11,Fhealth.
OL,13,FGiving evidence today, the CEO of
OL,14,FReading Refugee Support Group said he
OL,15,Fwrote to health and probation
OL,16,Fofficials to warn them that Khairi
OL,17,FSaadallah could commit a London Bridge
OL,18,Fstyle attack if he did not get
OL,19,Fappropriate help.
