OL,3,CAuthorities repeatedly warned about
OL,4,Cterrorist's mental health, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FSaadallah is currently serving a whole
OL,8,Flife order for the murders of James
OL,9,FFurlong, 36, David Wails, 49, and
OL,10,FJoseph Ritchie-Bennett, 39.
OL,12,FThree other men were injured during
OL,13,Fthe terrorist attack in the town's
OL,14,FForbury Gardens in June 2020.
OL,16,FThe inquest heard how Saadallah
OL,17,Fapproached Reading Refugee Support
OL,18,FGroup for help in September 2012.
