OL,3,CAuthorities repeatedly warned about
OL,4,Cterrorist's mental health, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FGiving evidence today the charity's
OL,8,FCEO Nick Harborne said following the
OL,9,Fincident he notified both probation
OL,10,Fand health officials that Saadallah
OL,11,Fwas at risk of radicalisation in
OL,12,Fprison and could commit a London
OL,13,FBridge style attack if he didn't
OL,14,Freceive the mental health support he
OL,15,Fneeded.
OL,17,FThe court heard these warnings were
OL,18,Fmade on numerous occasions including
OL,19,Fjust days before the attack in Reading
OL,20,Ftook place.
