OL,12,FIn one email to the NHS Berkshire West
OL,13,FClinical Commissioning Group, shown to
OL,14,Fthe court, Mr Harborne wrote:
OL,15,F"Prevent, probation, social services,
OL,16,Fthe community mental health team and
OL,17,Fthe rest of us have all let him down.
OL,18,FI am fearful if he doesn't get the
OL,19,Fright support for his trauma whilst in
OL,20,Fprison there could be disastrous
OL,21,Fconsequences."
