OL,7,FMr Harborne was asked "you felt no one
OL,8,Fwanted to take responsibility for an
OL,9,Faction plan for Khairi Saadallah
OL,10,Fcorrect?".
OL,12,FTo which he replied "yes and I felt we
OL,13,Fwere all letting him down".
OL,15,FThe scope of the inquest into their
OL,16,Fdeaths includes management of
OL,17,FSaadallah while he was in prison and
OL,18,Fhis mental health issues and the
OL,19,Fresponse to his risk of terrorism.
OL,21,FIt's due to conclude on 23 February.
